strings: <voice_0x01001CB7><se_high>Media princess: Is the end of the world near? What are you gonna do now!? what are we doing right
<voice_0x01001CB8><se_high>Media princess: Sorry, I lost control for a moment.
<voice_0x01001CB9><se_high>Media princess: I'm scared, but know that I'll go with you to the end of the world.
<voice_0x01001CBA><se_high>Media princess: I will do everything in my power to kill Rapson.
<voice_0x01001CBB><se_high>Media princess: As far as I know, the battle against Rapson began on the day of Dolmagot's accession to the throne.
<voice_0x01001CBC><se_high>Media princess: Now the sky was on fire and the whole world was scared...
<voice_0x01001CBD><se_high>Media princess: It's not just about your connection to the world anymore... the fate of it all is in your hands <hero>
<voice_0x01001CBE><se_high>Media princess: And no matter what, I will always be by your side!
